information: We source main A brands from most European Countries, depending on the country of origin, logistics, price and availability are fully optimized by our team. DOIberica is the export Division of a 50 year old Spanish distribution company focused on FMCG market. We are the main distributor of Dulcesol one of the biggest pastry manufacturers in Spain; AyC currently owns more than 8.000m3 of warehouses distributed across the east coast and inland, and delivers in the mornings and afternoons to 32.000 local clients. Well known Export company in Europe, with many years of experience, and clients from LATAM to Asia.
